title: Spyder Auto Installation: 2008-10 Honda Accord 4-Door Sedan DRL Projector Headlight
description: This video offers a step by step walkthrough for how to install a set of Spyder Projector Headlights on a 2008-10 Honda Accord 4-door sedan. For information on how to wire the Halo accessory, most users choose to wire the Halos into their parking lamps, see our video for how to wire LED Halo rings on our YouTube channel. This video is designed to guide you through the installation process, start to finish.
tags: Spyder Headlights, DRL, how to install, spyder lights, Honda Accord
